# Design System - 星辰序章 (Stellar Overture)

## Color Palette
- **bg-light**: #F8FAFC - Main background
- **bg-medium**: #E2E8F0 - Card/module background
- **text-dark**: #1E293B - Main text
- **accent-blue**: #0EA5E9 - Keywords/highlights
- **accent-orange**: #F97316 - Buttons/emphasis
- **accent-purple**: #A78BFA - Secondary/decorative
- **danger-red**: #EF4444 - Danger/warning
- **text-muted**: #64748B - Subdued text

## Typography
- **Serif Font**: System serif font for codex text
- **Sans Font**: System sans-serif font for UI elements

## Shadows
- **accent-glow**: 0 0 15px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4) - Blue glow for keywords
- **orange-glow**: 0 0 15px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4) - Orange glow for buttons

Always use these design tokens when implementing UI components to maintain visual consistency.